 disappears."--cProvided by publisher. 0aWomen librariansvFiction. 0aPhotographsvFiction. 0aCode and cipher stories. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xUnderground movementszFrancevFiction. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945zFrancevFiction. 0aJewszFrancevFiction. 0aFrancexHistoryyGerman occupation, 1940-1945vFiction. 0aLarge type books.  c(OCoLC)1193112290  c4640d4640